{"tid":312749,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回歸僅一年 董建華主動破壞一國兩制","createTime":"2017-07-07T17:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T17:06:32.000Z","uid":37111,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75bbcb3ee192ce426f97b58c933d5a41e6b2ef5e","tid":312749,"uid":37111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T17:06:32.000Z","msg":"片:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/702708179921253/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F702708179921253%2F&d=2JC1P%2FRpkAoTOlo1XAAattWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=4e4b73f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/702708179921253/</a><br />\n<br />\n全國政協副主席、香港首任特首董建華今午出席午餐會致辭時透露，亞洲金融風暴期間，香港政府在1998年曾出手入市打擊炒家，他事前曾致電已故的時任國務院副總理錢其琛，稱特區政府採取的一些救市措施，可能會影響內地，又指他們或會有盲點或不了解的地方，問中央可否派人來港，協助特區一同解決危機。<br />\n<br />\n兩日後錢其琛來電回覆董建華，拒絕其建議，稱他們都不太了解他和香港，貿貿然派人來港，或會給他一些錯誤的建議，「我和你都會後悔」，不認為這是好主意，相信他和其同事，著他安心去做。董建華續指，<strong>錢其琛向他重申，一國兩制之下中央不應派人來，反問他「你不記得嗎？」</strong>；董建華形容，是錢其琛提醒他不能這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n董建華上月底接受新華社訪問時，就表示「每當香港遇到困難的時候，都有國家作為強大的後盾」，包括亞洲金融風暴和2008年的國際金融危機等，得到國家的及時支持，而2003年爆發SARS時，中央領導曾問他香港有何要求，當他指醫療物資不足後，支援物資便隨即送到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/221909/%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%88%8697%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%82%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A9%E3%80%80%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%B6%E7%90%9B%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%EF%BC%9A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F221909%2F%25E8%2591%25A3%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%258F%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%258697%25E9%2587%2591%25E8%259E%258D%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%259B%25BE%25E9%2582%2580%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E7%259B%25B8%25E5%258A%25A9%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%258C%25A2%25E5%2585%25B6%25E7%2590%259B%25E6%258B%2592%25E7%25B5%2595%25EF%25BC%259A%2F&d=2JC1P%2FRpkAoTOlo1XAAattWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=bc89fee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/221909/%E8%91%A3%E5%BB%BA%E8%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%88%8697%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D%E9%A2%A8%E6%9A%B4%E6%9B%BE%E9%82%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E7%9B%B8%E5%8A%A9%E3%80%80%E9%8C%A2%E5%85%B6%E7%90%9B%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%EF%BC%9A/</a><br />\n<br />\n伸延閱讀:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060529/5969131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060529%2F5969131&d=2JC1P%2FRpkAoTOlo1XAAattWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=f67f050c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20060529%2F5969131&h=2709633c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20060529/5969131</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73473.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73473.jpg&h=8eff4ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請盡快離開人間"}]}